item.title: CVE-2023-2321|2024-08-02T06:19:14.920Z -- unknown -- wpforms%20google%20sheet%20connector
item.description: The WPForms Google Sheet Connector WordPress plugin before 3.4.6, gsheetconnector-wpforms-pro WordPress plugin through 3.4.6 does not escape a parameter before outputting it back in an attribute, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
